title: Sidewall
medium: Block-printed on handmade paper, joined sheets
description: Vertical rectangle with arabesque or grotesque design. Printed on joined sheets of paper. Alternating motifs: two addorsed griffins upholding a flower basket; female figures sheathed in foliage, resting upon a circular medallion enclosing a butterfly; cornucopia with flowers; branches, scrolls and pearls.
